                    <h3 class="about-founder-bio-section__name text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight !text-slate-900">Marko Pavlović</h3>
                    <span class="about-founder-bio-section__role mt-2 inline-flex items-center rounded-full !bg-[rgba(0,71,168,0.10)] px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold !text-[#0047A8]">Founder &amp; Lead Analyst</span>

                    <p class="about-founder-bio-section__bio mt-4 text-sm sm:text-base !text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
                        A data-driven analyst with a deep passion for combat sports. Marko combines statistical rigor with fight-specific domain knowledge to build scoring systems that reward real performance over narrative. With a background spanning statistical modeling, machine learning, and performance analytics, he has spent years dissecting fight data to uncover the patterns that traditional rankings miss. His work focuses on creating transparent, repeatable methodologies that put measurable outcomes above media-driven hype — giving fans and analysts alike a clearer picture of where fighters truly stand.
                    </p>

